Session_15:
==============

1. Write the code for the following scenario.
i. Create two classes(eg: Login, Search) and write 5 test cases in each class
ii. group 2 test cases as sanity and 3 test cases as regression in each class
iii. configure the testng.xml file to execute only regression test cases from Login and Search classes

2. Write the code for the following scenario.(here, configure parameters browser and url in testng.xml and use them)
i. Launch the application https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/web/index.php/auth/login in chrome browser before executing each test case
ii. Test case1: Verify the validation messages displayed when clicking on Login button without entering username and password.
iii. Test case2: Verify the validation message displayed when entering invalid credentials and clicking on Login button.
iv. Test case3: Verify the user is able to login to the application using valid credentials and redirects to Dashboard page.
v.  Test case4: Navigate to Admin page and validate all sub menu items from Job menu.
vi. Terminate the driver/browser session after executing each test case.

3. Write the code for the following scenario.(here, configure parameters browser and url in testng.xml and use them)
i. Create 3 test cases in a class for any scenarios in any web application
ii. Execute those test cases in chrome headless mode